  %h2 AsakusaSatellite
  %p
   AsakusaSatellite is a realtime chat application for Developers.
   Written with Ruby on Rails framework, MongoDB, WebKit notification.
  %p!='AsakusaSatellite is open source and released at <a href="https://github.com/codefirst/AsakusaSatellite">Github</a>.'

  %h2 Features
  %ul
   %li Realtime notification(using Websocket).
   %li Desktop notification.
   %li Flexible plugin extenension.
   %li Source code syntax highlight.
   %li Full text search.
   %li!='Collaboration with <a href="http://redmine.org/">Redmine</a>.'
   %li iPhone UI.

